Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:57.39,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I haven't been out in the boonies like this since I was a kid on school field trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:57.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな田舎来るのは\Nガキのころの遠足以来だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:02:00.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（滝川吉野）\N正確には　小３の遠足までだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.23,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,You mean since school field trips up until third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４年のころから\Nずる休みしてたじゃないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.84,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,You started skipping school in fourth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.25,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You remember weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:08.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　変なこと覚えてるのな。\N≫（子供）こっち　こっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.31,Default,KID A,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（子供）待てよ！\N（子供たち）あはははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.46,Default,KID B,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:16.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ～あ…　あんな\N靴　グチャグチャにしちゃって。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:16.16,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Man, look how dirty their shoes are getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.45,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,They probably don't care what's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界が\Nどんなになってるかなんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらには関係ないんだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおっ！\Nあっ　よけんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕たちにも　あんなころが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.24,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,We had times like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　なかったか。\Nそうだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.16,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,No, I guess we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.43,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Probably not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\N昔から　相当ひねくれてたし。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.30,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You've always been a bit of a rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ。　それは　こっちのセリフ。\Nへへっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.30,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.98,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,That's my line!
