Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.43,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(584,486)}Cursed Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ…　本殿の中に隠すなんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.93,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze hid this in the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さん　罰あたりだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.18,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,She's going to get cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　罰あたりが　もう一人。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.53,Default,YOsHINO,0,0,0,,And then we have another cursed one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなの　ただの置物だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.66,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Who cares? It's just some decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N私の神は　はじまりの樹だけだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.34,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,My only god is the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.74,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,I know nothing of other gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの神など知らん。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.74,Default,YosHINO,0,0,0,,Right, of course you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうですよね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:09.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雨か…　面倒だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.17,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Rain? That's gonna be annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　折り畳み傘を持ってきて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.01,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.49,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I brought a travel umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,旅行じゃないんだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.17,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,We aren't on a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:17.04,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I'd rather you said that I'm well prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用意周到って\N言ってほしいんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広！\Nおう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:18.80,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Mahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.38,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:24.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと面倒なもんが来やがった！\N（葉風・通信）果実か!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.64,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,We have something even more annoying to deal with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.64,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,A fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.72,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,The last one flew just three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N前回　飛んだのは３日前だぞ！→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.47,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Damn you, Samon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門め　儀式を早めるリスクより→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.44,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's more afraid of me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の手が伸びる方を恐れたか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.93,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,than of any risk from hurrying the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.73,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,堅実好みのヤツらしいが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（老人）降ってきたなぁ。\Nこいつぁ　激しくなるかもしれんて。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.98,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,It's starting to rain a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.69,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,It could start pouring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（老人）ハウスの鍵　締めてこんと。\N教えなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.71,Default,GRAMS,0,0,0,,Better lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:41.92,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I've got to warn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.49,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,{\3c&H20271B&}There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）間に合わん！\Nおい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:42.49,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.95,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,They'll be okay as long as I have the talisman and they're close by, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔具を持ってる僕のそばにいれば\N大丈夫なんでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）あれは事なかれ主義の\N冷静な男に見えていたが→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.45,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,I thought he could stay calm, no matter the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案外　熱血漢なのか？\Nさあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.20,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,But is he somewhat rash instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.83,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.69,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,There's something about him that I'll never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは\Nよく分からねぇとこがあるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:01.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？　黒鉄…　病？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.05,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.15,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,Black Iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.34,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,Syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:05.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！　すぐに避難してください！\N周りの人にも呼びかけて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.56,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.17,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Please get to safety immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.73,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,And let others know along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（老人）\Nほらほら　忙しいんだ。　邪魔だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.62,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,We're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.08,Default,GRAMPS,0,0,0,,Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.22,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってください！\N信じろってのが無理だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.35,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You can't expect them to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒鉄病については\N政府が隠蔽している。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.06,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,The government is hiding everything about Black Iron Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.28,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,This is worse than some fairytale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとぎ話より　たちが悪い。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:23.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって　このまま\N何もしないで見過ごすなんて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.25,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,But for us to do nothing and watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪（子供）すげぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.49,Default,KID A,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.95,Default,KID A,0,0,0,,Isn't that a purple swallowtail butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（子供）\Nあれ　ムラサキアゲハじゃね？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ　すごい！\Nあっ　あそこにも　たくさん。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:29.93,Default,KID B,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.52,Default,KID B,0,0,0,,Wow, there are lots over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.52,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,The talisman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔具を…。\N≪ゴゴゴゴゴッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:09.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野！\Nうっ…　くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.24,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気にするな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.57,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.94,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,They just couldn't find a way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらは　生き残る術を\N見つけられなかっただけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:04.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんくださ～い。　すいませ～ん。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.31,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:03.92,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしも～し。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.42,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:11.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫誰もいないんですね。\Nじゃあ　裏口から失礼しま～す。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.94,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,No one's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.05,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Then we're coming through the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ガチャ（ドアの音）\N≫おい　真広　人の家だぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.95,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Hey, Mahiro, this is someone's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.68,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,If they're hard as a rock, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちにしろ\Nカチンカチンになってるだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.31,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,We can't do anything in this rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この雨じゃ　身動き取れねぇんだし\N休んでいこうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.98,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,so we might as well rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって…。\Nおっ　なんだ　これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.44,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.03,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:23.88,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't flush with water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水洗じゃないのか。　初めて見た。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.78,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I've never seen that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼します。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.07,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Pardon our intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.27,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Oh, a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫おっ　風呂だ。　ありがたいなぁ\Nすっかり冷えちまったから。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... I feel like an ice cube.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:38.91,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！\N勝手に風呂は　さすがに…　って→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.96,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,A bath is pushing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.70,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,You already undressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう脱いでる!?\Nああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.17,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.68,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:48.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ\N野郎と一緒に入る趣味はねぇぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.42,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I've no interest in bathing with another guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！\Nなっ…　シャワーないのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.44,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Whoa! There's no shower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.56,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,By the way, Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）ところで　吉野。\Nなんでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.27,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:09.57,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,It's all right to use their kitchen, but not their bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N風呂を借りるのはダメで→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,台所を借りるのは　よしなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.45,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't going to end anytime soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから\N長丁場になりますからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:19.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,栄養は　しっかりとらないと。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.96,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,We have to keep our energy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N真広は　まだ出てこないのか？→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.92,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Mahiro still isn't out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:27.10,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Taking a long bath in a village just cursed by the fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果実にやられた村で長風呂とは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）時に吉野。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.74,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,By the way, Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:34.04,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,How long have you and Mahiro known each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と真広は\Nいつからのつきあいなのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小学校からですかね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.74,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Since elementary school, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\Nふむ。　どうも　真広とお前は→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:44.23,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,One wouldn't normally imagine you two as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通に友達には\Nなりそうな感じがせんのだがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.94,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,We weren't friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達じゃなかったんですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.94,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,He's smart and good at sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:53.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは\N頭も運動神経もいいけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.13,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,but he always looked down on those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:56.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りを　どこか\N小バカにしたように見てて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.41,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Sounds hard to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N手を焼きそうな子供だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふっ。　ただ→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:04.22,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,But it wasn't all his fault, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:04.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部　真広の責任ってわけでも\Nないんですけどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.08,Default,TEACH,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師・回想）((おはよう))\N（生徒）((おはようございます))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.85,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）((おはよう))\N((おはようございます))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:07.46,Default,TEACH,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.18,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Good morn—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.92,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Mahiro's father was a pretty prominent figure back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:16.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広の父親は\N地元じゃ　有名な名士でしたから→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.01,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校としても\N下手に真広を注意して→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the school couldn't admonish Mahiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.62,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,since they were worried about trouble with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:23.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親から　どなり込まれでもしたら\N大変ですし→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:26.57,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,The other kids got that feeling, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:27.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの生徒も\Nそんな空気は感じていて…→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと浮いた存在でしたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.57,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,So he was sort of in a different league.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\Nお前の性格からすると→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.10,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Judging by your personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd think that you would avoid someone like Mahiro even if you weren't asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼まれなくても\N真広みたいのは避けるであろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　避けてましたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.58,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Yes, I avoided him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ\Nちょっとした事件があったんです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.42,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,But then something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よいしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:05.85,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,It was when we were in third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:06.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは　僕たちが\N小学校３年のときでした。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:16.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バイクに乗った　ひったくり犯が\N警察の車に追われ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.86,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,The police were chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a mugger on a motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.13,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Maybe the mugger simply wasn't paying enough attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハンドル操作をミスしたのか\N歩道を　一人歩いていた真広に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.54,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Still, he ran into Mahiro who was walking alone on the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（吉野の父）\N((犯人は　重体だってさ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.54,Default,DAD,0,0,0,,The mugger is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ意識は戻らないって))\N（吉野の母）((わあ～　怖～い。→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.65,Default,DAD,0,0,0,,He's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.52,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Oh, how scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.52,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,But it's good that Mahiro escaped with only a few broken bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも真広君は　骨折で済んだんなら\Nよかったわよね。→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ\Nこら　吉野　またセロリ残して…))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:50.68,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.57,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Are you leaving your celery again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:56.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((マヨネーズ　いっぱい掛けてから\N食べようと思った))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.97,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I was going to put mayonnaise on them and then eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:59.00,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,You'll never grow big if you're a picky eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（吉野の母）((好き嫌いが多いと\N大きくなれないよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.36,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I don't hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:02.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((嫌いじゃない。　苦手なだけ))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:05.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（吉野の父）\N((吉野　真広君と仲がいいのか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.10,Default,DAD,0,0,0,,Yoshino,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.40,Default,DAD,0,0,0,,are you friends with Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:10.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ううん　僕　あいつ苦手なんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.41,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.77,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((見た　見た？　テレビ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.10,Default,KID A,0,0,0,,Did you see on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((隣のクラスの相沢も\Nちょっとテレビに出てたぞ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.86,Default,KID B,0,0,0,,Aizawa, from the next class, was on for just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.30,Default,KID C,0,0,0,,Awesome, he's totally famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((すげぇ！　有名人！))\N（教師）((は～い　静かに！→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.42,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.97,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,I'm sure Fuwa is lonely, stuck in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:21.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破も\N入院で寂しいだろうからな→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生と一緒に　誰か代表で\Nお見舞いに行ってくれる人))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:25.61,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Who will represent the class and go visit him along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）\N((お見舞いに行ってくれる人))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.44,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Who will go visit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((だって\Nどうせ　あいつ喜ばないし))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.67,Default,KID A,0,0,0,,It's not like he'd be happy if we went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:35.21,Default,KID B,0,0,0,,Yeah, he'd probably ask what the heck we're doing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:34.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((そうそう\Nなんで来やがったとか言いそう))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.64,Default,KID C,0,0,0,,He totally would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((だよね～))\N（教師）((お前らなぁ…。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.78,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys...
