Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなも心配してたぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.72,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,You're pretty lucky, considering how serious the accident was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）((ほんと　あれだけの\N事故だったのに運がよかったな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.70,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,I heard the bike was totaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バイクも何も　大破したって…))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((先生))\N（教師）((ん？　どうした))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.38,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.49,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ジュース飲みたい))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.68,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I'd like something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:09.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((おっ　そうか　特別だぞ？\Nみんなには　ないしょな))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.80,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.61,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,This is special, so don't tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あっ　あの…　先生…))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.31,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,U-Um, Teach—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((≫バタン（ドアの音）))\N((はぁ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((悪いが頼みがある))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.17,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I hate to ask, but I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((頼みだよ　聞こえてんだろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.76,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,A request...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((え…　え～っと→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.04,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:33.02,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I was sort of forced into coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は　渋々　嫌々\Nお見舞いに来ただけで→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上　君とは　関わり合いに\Nなりたくないんだけど))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.92,Default,YOSHINo,0,0,0,,so I'd rather not deal with you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((正直なヤツだな))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.05,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That's way too blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.74,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,And so, if you have a request,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:41.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そういうことで\N頼みは　先生か　お父さんに…))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.91,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,could you ask the teacher or your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((だから　大人じゃ　まともに\N聞いてもらえそうにねぇから→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:45.70,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Listen. Adults won't take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ　お前に頼んでんだよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.55,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:54.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺の事故の状況とか\N犯人のこととか→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.79,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I want you to research the circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.90,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,surrounding my accident and the mugger as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるかぎり調べて教えろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そんなの知って　どうするの？))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.11,Default,YOsHINO,0,0,0,,And what will you do with that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺に突っ込んできた\Nひったくり犯→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.69,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,The mugger that crashed into me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは　わざとだよ))\N((はあ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:03.86,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.12,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺を殺す気で→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.10,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He was trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を狙って突っ込んできたんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.04,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He aimed at me, and then he crashed into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あのとき　ヘルメットで→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.82,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.45,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I couldn't see his expression because of his helmet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,表情が分からなかったけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.92,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,but I felt the bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに殺気がしたんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:32.09,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He mugged someone and purposely got chased by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:30.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((たぶん　ひったくりを\N警察に見つかって→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げているところで\N運悪く俺をひき殺したって→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.94,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,so he could "accidentally" run me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せかけようとしたんだ→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.69,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That way, he could hide the real reason for killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を殺す\N本当の理由を隠すために))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そこまで分かってるなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.04,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you should tell the police or your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,警察とか　お父さんに\Nそう言えばいいじゃないか))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:49.44,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Adults won't act just because I said I felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺が感じただけで\N大人は動かねぇ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.82,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That's why I have to look for clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((だからこそ\N手がかりを探してんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((で　なんで　僕が…))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.00,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.31,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Because I don't have anyone else I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ほかに頼めるヤツが\Nいねぇんだよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.88,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,But that's because you don't have any frie—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:59.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((それは　君に\N友達がいないからじゃ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.50,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((うるせぇ！\Nお前こそ　どうなんだよ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.74,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What about you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.65,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Even though we're in the same class,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺と一緒のクラスっていう割に\N全然覚えがねぇぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember ever seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((名前も思い出せねぇ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:07.27,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I can't even remember your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.80,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Does a guy who leaves such a shallow impression even have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そんな影の薄いヤツに\N友達がいんのか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.47,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Is that the attitude you should have when asking for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((それが\N人に物を頼む態度かい？))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.66,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((お前こそ\N入院してるクラスメイトに→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.57,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Don't you feel you should be at least a little nice to a hospitalized classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優しくしようって気は\N起きねぇのか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.98,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そんな…))\N((≫ガラガラ（ドアの音）))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.33,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like you guys are having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）((おっ？　なんか\Nにぎやかだな　仲いいじゃないか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.36,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Great to see you getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってろよ\N今　コップについでやる))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.95,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Wait a sec, and I'll pour a cup for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((うわっ！))\N((先生))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.31,Default,mAHIRO,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.65,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He said he'd come visit me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((こいつ　また来てくれるって))\N((ええ～!?))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.53,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.65,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）\N((そうか！　よかった　よかった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.97,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,That's great to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.97,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Friends are the best medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達ってのはさ\N何よりの薬だからな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:40.21,Default,TEACHER,0,0,0,,I had a feeling that you two would hit it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生は\Nお前ら　合うと思ってたんだよ～))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ごちそうさま))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.57,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（吉野の母）((もう　ごちそうさま？\Nちゃんと　野菜食べたの？→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.64,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,You're already done?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.78,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Did you eat all your vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あら…))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.24,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((苦手なものは\N先に食べちゃうことにしたんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.87,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I decided to eat everything I don't like first.
