Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((とりあえず\Nこれだけ調べてきたよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.38,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,This is all I have for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((これ　全部　お前一人で？))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:01.91,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.91,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You did all this alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:09.79,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I'm not like you, just acting on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:07.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((君みたいに\N勘だけで何かしようとか→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうのは　どうかと思うんだ))\N((ふん))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((これが　犯人の人の証明写真))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.16,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,This is a picture of the mugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そっちは　住んでるアパート))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.36,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,That's his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あっ　あと\N君のお父さんの会社の→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:21.31,Default,YoshINO,0,0,0,,Oh, and I got a pamphlet from your father's workplace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パンフレットを\Nもらってきたんだけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:25.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この人\N君ん家の運転手の人でしょ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:25.31,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,This guy is your chauffeur, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ん？　ああ\Nこんな顔のヤツいたっけな))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:29.06,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He doesn't look familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:32.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((前に一度\N学校に　君の送迎に来てたから→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.05,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I remember him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because he came to pick you up at school once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:36.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えていたんだ))\N((お前　変なこと覚えてるのな))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:37.02,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You remember weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((たぶん　こないだ　父さんに\N辞めさせられちゃったヤツだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.77,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,He's probably the guy my dad fired the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((こいつが　どうした？))\N((たぶん　この人が犯人だよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.36,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.03,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I think he's the one behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ふ～ん…　ん？))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((はあ!?　あっ！　いっ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:48.90,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((具合悪いんだから\N落ち着きなよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.90,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,You aren't feeling well, so you should calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((どうして\Nこいつが犯人になるんだ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.87,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Why would it be him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((もし犯人が\Nひったくり犯のふりをして→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:02.23,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,If the guy responsible had impersonated a mugger
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to cause the accident on purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:06.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざと事故を起こしたんならさ\N君の通学路とか→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.23,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,The plan wouldn't go well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:10.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寄り道するルートとか知ってないと\Nうまくいかないよね))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,unless he knew exactly which roads you take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.88,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,And since you don't trust anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((でも\Nうたぐり深い君のことじゃあ→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:17.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君を調べてる人がいたら\Nすぐに気付きそうなものだし))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:16.84,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,you'd probably notice if someone was researching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((微妙にケンカ売ってるだろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:19.32,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,You're trying to pick a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:23.08,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,But if it's someone who always took you to and from school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:23.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((でも　いつも\N君を送り迎えしてる人だったら…))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((それで　ちょっと調べたら\Nこの二人　知り合いだったんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.70,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,So I did a little research,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.95,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,and these two knew each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.30,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I don't know their relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((理由とかは\Nよく分からないけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:37.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君のお父さんは　この人から\N恨みを買っていたんだと思う))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:37.10,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,but I think he held a grudge against your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((その復讐で\N息子を殺そうとして→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.42,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,To get revenge, he tried to kill you, the son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知っている人に\N手伝わせたんだと思うよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.28,Default,YOsHINO,0,0,0,,And he asked someone he knew to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.09,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.62,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((電話　取ってくれ))\N((えっ？　手　届くよね？))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.75,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Could you hand me the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:53.13,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Huh? But you can reach, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.31,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I'm pissed, so could you just grab it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((なんか　むかつくから取れよ))\N((はあ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.47,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.97,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Hello, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:09.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あっ　父さん？　うん))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:10.27,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あの…　犯人　分かったんだけど))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.04,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,I found out who was behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N犯人を調べろと言われて→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.02,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,He asked you to look into the mugger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真犯人まで当ててしまったのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.38,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,and you ended up identifying the actual mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当てたってほど\N大げさなものじゃあ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.78,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,That's a bit of an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:23.64,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Besides, I wanted to hurry up and find the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに　早いとこ\N真犯人を見つけたかったんです→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広から解放されたくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.63,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I wanted to get away from Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N厄介事から逃げるためか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.31,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,So it was to escape the burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　お前らしいが。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.35,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,That does sound like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当初の計画では\N犯人は　真広をひき殺して→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.86,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,In the original plan, the mugger was meant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げきる\N予定だったみたいなんです。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:36.21,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,to run over and kill Mahiro, then escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:40.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃走に手を貸すよう　コンテナ車とか\N準備していたみたいなんですけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:40.43,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Apparently, they even readied an 18-wheeler to aid in the the escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.69,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,But Mahiro had the devil's own luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:43.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\Nそこが　真広の悪運の強さか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:48.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほどな。　それで\Nお前と真広は　仲よくなったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.69,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.79,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,And so you two became friends afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ。　僕は　もう→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:49.30,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.17,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I didn't want anything to do with him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:53.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつには\N関わる気がなかったんですが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.42,#staff,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\frx5\fry0\c&H474747&\xshad-1.5\yshad-1.8\fscx213\fscy212\pos(666,522)\org(384,531)}S{\xshad-1.1}t{\xshad-0.7}a{\xshad-0.5}f{\xshad-0.2}f {\xshad0.6}R{\xshad0.8}o{\xshad1.1}o{\xshad1.3}m
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:57.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）((いや～！　吉野が\Nこんなに仲よくなるなんてなぁ))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.40,Default,TEACH,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you'd get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((だから　仲よくなんて…))\N（教師）((先生　すっごくうれしいぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.46,Default,YOSHINO,600,0,0,,But I didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.46,Default,TEACH,0,600,0,,I'm very proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.14,Nyarlko?,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.3\fsp1\blur0.8\frx26\fry358\frz334.4\fscx198\fscy110\alpha&H35&\pos(740,150)},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.14,Nyarlko?,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.5\fsp1\blur0.8\frx26\fry358\pos(774,193)\frz334.4\fscx198\fscy110\alpha&H30&}Ma{\fax-0.52}hiro{\alpha&HFF&},{\alpha&H30&\fax-0.55}s {\fax-0.6\c&H222222&}Guar{\fax-0.64\c&H1A1A1A&}dian
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.14,Default,TEACH,0,0,0,,From today on, I'm putting you in charge of Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）\N((今日から　真広係に任命する！))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.14,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,In charge... of Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((真広…　係))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:13.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕と一緒にさせておけば\N真広は　おとなしくしてるし→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:13.10,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Apparently, he thought that if Mahiro were around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざというとき　抑えも利くって\N思われたらしくて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.68,Default,YosHINO,0,0,0,,he wouldn't act out and could be managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.48,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,And from then through junior high, we shared the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから\Nクラスは　中学まで　ずっと一緒。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人１組で行動するときも\N全部　あいつと一緒にされて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.14,Default,YOsHINO,0,0,0,,If we had to choose partners,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.95,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I'd automatically get paired with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）それは　災難だったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.31,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく　そのとおりです。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.86,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I couldn't have said it better myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:35.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ　真広は　周りから\N嫌われていたっていうより→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:35.29,Default,YOSHInO,0,0,0,,However, rather than Mahiro being hated by those around him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.40,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I think he was actually admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらかというと\N憧れられていたと思います。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:43.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでもできて\N好き放題に行動して→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:43.47,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,He could do anything, and did whatever he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも不敵に　身勝手に生きて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.15,Default,YOShINO,0,0,0,,He always lived fearlessly, however he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達になりたい子も\N多かったと思います。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:50.01,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,I'm sure a lot of kids wanted to be friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:53.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　真広は\N容易に人を寄せつけませんから。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:54.00,Default,YOSHIno,0,0,0,,But Mahiro wouldn't let people in easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子供だって　真広みたいなのに\N不用意に近づけば→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:18:00.32,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Even kids could see that if they tried to get close to someone like him, they'd get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に傷つくことがある\Nってことぐらい分かる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.06,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,So for better or worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:06.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）幸か不幸か　真広に\N不用意に近づいてしまったのが→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you ended up being the one who recklessly got close to Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前というわけか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広に関わったせいで\N僕も遠くに来たもんですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:12.49,Default,YosHINO,0,0,0,,But I got pretty far because I was close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:16.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠くへ…　か。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.81,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は　遠くへ行けるから\N真広と関われたのだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.79,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,It's because you were able to go far that you could put up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ　違いがありますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.44,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Is there a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\Nないと思う方が　どうかしている。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:25.02,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,If you don't think so, there's something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\N≫ああ～→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい湯だった。　おっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.42,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That was a great bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メシか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:30.89,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不合理なメシだな。　はぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.03,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Even if it looks weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:44.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで\N味噌汁にセロリが入ってんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.51,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Why is there celery in the miso soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通は　セロリは生だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.40,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Celery is usually eaten raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生で食べると苦いんだよ。\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.61,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,It's bitter if you eat it raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:50.84,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静かだ。\N田舎だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.73,Default,YosHINO,0,0,0,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.31,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Well, we're in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけじゃないよ。\N虫の声もしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.38,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,It's not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even hear cows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ　みんな　黒鉄病で…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.31,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Probably because of the Black Iron Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや\N蝶は　なんで大丈夫なんだ？　葉風。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.76,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,By the way, why aren't the butterflies affected, Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昼寝か？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.10,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Napping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のんきなもんだよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.52,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Must be nice to be so carefree...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのさ　真広。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.36,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,Hey, Mahiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ…　なんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.82,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty carefree, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分だって\Nのんきなもんじゃないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:09.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ザッザッザッ（足音）\N（葉風・通信）朝の散歩か？→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.39,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Taking a morning walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前にも\N風情の分かる心があったとはな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.85,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Who knew you were capable of enjoying such quaint activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャリン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）その音…\N飲料水を手に入れるのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.22,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:20.53,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,So now you're actually using money to get drinking water?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を使うようになったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:25.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蹴っただけじゃあ\N何が出るか分からないからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:24.51,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Well, who knows what you'll end up with if you just kick the vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.36,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.89,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,How long have you and Yoshino known each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と吉野は\Nいつからのつきあいなのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふわぁ～。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:39.18,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,There was some stupid accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くだらねぇ事故があって\Nくだらねぇ結果になって→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and it had stupid results...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ\Nいろいろあっての腐れ縁だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.11,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,And then other things happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've been together since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N「くだらねぇ」ばかりだな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.58,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Sounds like everything was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事故の件は　吉野から聞いたが。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.15,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Yoshino told me about the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:52.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ。\Nだったら　わざわざ　俺に聞くなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.58,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't need to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.91,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,The story has a stupid punch line, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:56.58,whitepowder,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur1\alpha&H50&\frx0\fry10\org(492,984)\pos(621,451)}Es{\fax-0.08}say {\fax-0.03}Pre{\fax-0.01}sen{\fax0}ta{\fax0.03}tion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれには　くだらねぇオチもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((「真広君が　バイクに\Nひかれそうになったのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.92,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,The reason Mahiro got hit by a motorcycle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.64,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,was because he was trying to save a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子犬を　とっさに\N助けようとしたからです。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:06.56,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,He then asked me to find the puppy's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は　助けた子犬の飼い主を\N探すように頼まれました。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広君は　本当は\Nとっても優しい人です」))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.43,Default,YOSHINO,0,0,0,,In reality, Mahiro is a very nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）\N((す…　す…　すばらしい！→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:13.33,Default,TEACH,0,0,0,,H-H-How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:18.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな　不破に拍手～！))\N（生徒）((すげぇじゃん　真広って))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.72,Default,TEACH,0,0,0,,Let's have a round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.13,Default,KID,0,0,0,,Mahiro's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.30,Default,KID2,0,0,0,,Who knew he was such a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒）((へえ～　いい人だったんだ))\N((ふふっ))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:25.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから　クラスの俺を見る目が\N変に生暖かくなって→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:25.91,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,After that, everyone in class started acting weird and nice toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれだけ　居心地悪かったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.79,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Talk about uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.71,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,I see. This story is vaguely unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\Nなるほど　微妙に嫌な話だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:34.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野は　あんな顔して\N性格が悪いって知ったのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:34.38,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,That was when I learned how vicious Yoshino is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.04,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,despite his innocent face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがきっかけだったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.72,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,So it was his way of getting back at you for being forced to deal with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:40.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広に\N嫌々つきあわされた意趣返しか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）なんだよ。\Nいや…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.51,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:42.77,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering what would have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし\N貴様と吉野が出会わなかったら→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなっていただろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hadn't met Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.14,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野と出会わなかったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）何も変わらんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.24,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Nothing would have changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:57.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら　こんな遠くへは\N来れなかったかもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.11,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,It's possible that I might never have made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふっ。\N（通信）だから　なんだってんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:01.11,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Seriously, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.09,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,My apologies. It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）すまん　なんでもない。\Nちょっとな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:07.24,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:11.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,訳分からねぇ。　はぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.10,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）ん？　どうした。\Nいや　なんでもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:17.68,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:20.38,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Nothing.
