Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:12.32,Default,MAHIRO,0,0,0,,Pretty confident, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:15.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nそうだ　それさえも導かれた運命。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:15.60,Default,HAKAZE,0,0,0,,That's right... That, too, was guided by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）左門殿に\Nまたとない手土産ができそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:19.52,Default,GUY,0,0,0,,It appears I'll have a unique gift for Mr. Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:23.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）これも　いつかは\N美しい結末の伏線になるでしょう。
